OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775127595
OL,3,C'Lives ruined in an instant' in
OL,4,Ccrashes as PSNI issue Easter road
OL,5,Csafety message
OL,7,FThe PSNI has said it will be clamping
OL,8,Fdown on dangerous driving over Easter,
OL,9,Fas part of an ongoing campaign to
OL,10,Freduce deaths on Northern Ireland's
OL,11,Froads.
OL,13,FTwenty people have lost their lives on
OL,14,Fthe roads so far this year which is
OL,15,Fdouble the number during the same
OL,16,Fperiod in 2025.
OL,18,FWith traffic expected to increase over
OL,19,Fthe Easter period, speed enforcement
OL,20,Fis set to continue with Operation
OL,21,FLifesaver patrols.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
