FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775127595
OL,3,C'Lives ruined in an instant' in
OL,4,Ccrashes as PSNI issue Easter road
OL,5,Csafety message
OL,7,FAccording to PSNI statistics, by
OL,8,FTuesday there had been 20 people
OL,9,Fkilled on the roads compared to 10 by
OL,10,FMarch 31 in 2025, and 15 by March 31
OL,11,Fin 2024.
OL,13,FPolice have also reminded those
OL,14,Ftravelling to wear seatbelts,
OL,15,Frevealing that officers made 559
OL,16,Fdetections for seatbelts not being
OL,17,Fworn between December 2024 and
OL,18,FNovember 2025.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775127595
OL,3,C'Lives ruined in an instant' in
OL,4,Ccrashes as PSNI issue Easter road
OL,5,Csafety message
OL,7,FThey also warned about the dangers of
OL,8,Fusing a mobile phone or device while
OL,9,Fdriving, saying that between December
OL,10,F2024 and November 2025, 1,060 drivers
OL,11,Fwere detected using their phone behind
OL,12,Fthe wheel.
OL,14,FPSNI Head of Road Policing, Chief
OL,15,FInspector Celeste Simpson described
OL,16,Fthe number of deaths as "devastating"
OL,17,Fand said there are "too many lives
OL,18,Fruined forever and in an instant".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775127595
OL,3,C'Lives ruined in an instant' in
OL,4,Ccrashes as PSNI issue Easter road
OL,5,Csafety message
OL,7,FShe said: "Our roads are a shared
OL,8,Fspace and it's crucial we all work
OL,9,Ftogether to reduce risk taking and
OL,10,Fpoor behaviour on our roads.
OL,12,F"To all drivers, we are appealing to
OL,13,Fyou to work with us to help make our
OL,14,Froads safer for everyone.
OL,16,F"Our officers will be on patrol during
OL,17,Fthis period to increase road safety
OL,18,Fand tackle the Fatal Five, the main
OL,19,Freasons people are dying on our roads.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
