PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775127595
OL,3,C'Lives ruined in an instant' in
OL,4,Ccrashes as PSNI issue Easter road
OL,5,Csafety message
OL,7,F"Take a few minutes before you drive
OL,8,Foff and think about how you want your
OL,9,Fcar journey to end.
OL,11,F"Driving requires your undivided
OL,12,Fattention. Take your eyes off the road
OL,13,Ffor even a few seconds and it could
OL,14,Fmean the difference between an
OL,15,Fenjoyable weekend break and a tragedy
OL,16,Fyou have to live with for the rest of
OL,17,Fyour lives."
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,20,FITVX
